sketch.compiler.main.cmdline

Class SketchOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.main.cmdline.SketchOptions
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ParallelSketchOptions, SMTSketchOptions

    public class SketchOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    organized options for the new clojure frontend, which replaces most frontends. See ParallelSketchOptions for how to inherit options effectively and concisely.
    Author:
    gatoatigrado (nicholas tung) [email: ntung at ntung]
